title: Danish Concussion victim find healing in Jordan Peterson Videos
description:
Lars is a Danish engineer. He learned skills suffering from depression that were valuable in dealing with a severe concussion. What was fascinating was how Jordan Peterson videos helped the healing from his concussion.
